    "html": "<div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;background:var(--surface-dark);background-color:var(--surface-dark);overflow:hidden;\">\n            <div style=\"position: absolute; opacity: 0.04; z-index: 1; background: var(--texture-grain); pointer-events: none; inset: 0\"></div>\n            \n            <div class=\"slide-content\" style=\"position:relative;z-index:10;padding:80px var(--space-6) 80px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;height:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;\">\n                <div style=\"width:100%;height:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:flex-start;\">\n            <div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:230px;border-radius:var(--radius-md);overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);border:1px solid #242F3D30;\">\n                <div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:240px;border-radius: var(--radius-sm);overflow:hidden;background:transparent;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n                <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1451187580459-43490279c0fa?w=600\" alt=\"Annotated Diagram\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit: cover; object-position: center;filter: contrast(1.06) brightness(1.06);\" />\n                \n            </div>\n                \n            </div>\n            <p style=\"font-family:Outfit;font-size:12px;color:#C7CED8;margin:10px 0 0;line-height:1.45;opacity:0.9;\">Reciprocity is why free content converts better than paid advertising.</p>\n            <div style=\"margin-top:10px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;width:100%;\"><div style=\"font-family:Outfit;font-size:12px;color:#C7CED8;line-height:1.45;\">\n                        <strong style=\"color:#EAEFF5;font-weight:700;\">Principle #1: Reciprocity</strong> \u2014 Give value first. The audience feels obligated to reciprocate \u2014 with attention, engagement, or action.\n                    </div></div>\n        </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
