    "html": "<div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;background:radial-gradient(at 40% 20%, #1565C015 0px, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(at 80% 0%, #9A540010 0px, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(at 0% 50%, #62ADFF12 0px, transparent 50%), var(--surface-light);background-color:var(--surface-light);overflow:hidden;\">\n            <div style=\"background: var(--texture-grain); inset: 0; pointer-events: none; opacity: 0.04; position: absolute; z-index: 1\"></div>\n            \n            <div class=\"slide-content\" style=\"position:relative;z-index:10;padding:80px 48px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;height:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;\">\n                <div style=\"width:100%;\"><h2 style=\"font-family: Fraunces; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.18; color: #080B0F; margin: 0 0 16px; text-align: left; letter-spacing: -0.01em; overflow-wrap: break-word\">Myth vs Fact</h2><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;width:100%;\"><div style=\"background:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #C4CBD425;border-radius:0;padding:12px 14px;margin-bottom:12px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);position:relative;flex-shrink:0;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-family:Outfit;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#3D434A;text-decoration:line-through;text-decoration-color:#1565C0;text-decoration-thickness:2px;opacity:0.6;line-height:1.35;\">Scarcity and urgency are the same thing</div>\n                    <div style=\"position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(-6deg);font-family:Fraunces;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;color:#EFF6FF;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;background:#1565C0;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px;box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);\">MYTH</div>\n                </div><div style=\"background:#EFF6FF;border-left:4px solid #1565C0;border:1px solid #C4CBD425;border-left-width:4px;border-radius:0;padding:12px 14px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);flex-shrink:0;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-family:Fraunces;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;color:#1565C0;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:4px;\">FACT</div>\n                    <div style=\"font-family:Outfit;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#080B0F;line-height:1.35;\">Scarcity is about limited supply; urgency is about limited time. Combined, they create the most powerful persuasion force in marketing.</div>\n                </div><div style=\"font-family:Outfit;font-size:13px;color:#3D434A;margin-top:14px;line-height:1.45;\">The best CTAs use both: &#x27;Only 3 spots left&#x27; (scarcity) + &#x27;Offer ends tonight&#x27; (urgency). Together they&#x27;re exponentially more effective.</div></div></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
